      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving straight-six maintains excellent compression across all cylinders, with the dual-VANOS system recently overhauled to ensure precise cam phasing. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings and updated dampers, and the critical rear subframe mounting points have been inspected and reinforced for structural longevity. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping consistent with an enthusiast-driven life, the mechanical vitals\u2014including the individual throttle bodies and cooling system\u2014are in excellent operational order. This is a driver-spec example optimized for tactile feedback and longitudinal performance.",
